---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const articleHtml = `<p>Existing HedgeFlows users who want to integrate their HedgeFlows account with Netsuite can do so via the <strong>Settings</strong> page as follows:</p> 
 <h3>1) Locate NetSuite Integration</h3> <p>Locate NetSuite in the <strong>Accounting system integrations</strong> section of our Settings page and click on "Connect":</p> <p><img src="https://help.hedgeflows.com/hs-fs/hubfs/netsuite_1.png" alt="netsuite_1" width="1832" height="932" loading="lazy"></p> <h3>2) Connect to ORACLE NetSuite</h3> <p>You should see the integration pop-up window informing you about the type of information we will access from NetSuite when authorising HedgeFlows connection to your NetSuite account. </p> <p><img src="https://help.hedgeflows.com/hs-fs/hubfs/netsuite_2.png" alt="netsuite_2" width="514" height="464" loading="lazy"></p> <h3>3) Install your NetSuite Bundle</h3> <p>You must first infall a bundle that connects HedgeFlows to NetSuite. You must have Administrator rights in NetSuite to install bundles. Click on the link to access bundles, search for AppLink and click to install.</p> <p><img src="https://help.hedgeflows.com/hs-fs/hubfs/nesuite_3.png" alt="nesuite_3" width="544" height="658" loading="lazy"></p> <h3>4) Enable SuiteCloud features</h3> <p>Your connection will fail if the following instructions are not completed, these features allow us to connect to your NetSuite account:</p> <p><img src="https://help.hedgeflows.com/hs-fs/hubfs/netsuite_4.png" alt="netsuite_4" width="547" height="718" loading="lazy"></p> <h3>5) Confirm link setup</h3> <p>Please confirm you have installed the NetSuite bundle and Enabled selected features.</p> <p><img src="https://help.hedgeflows.com/hs-fs/hubfs/netsuite_5.png" alt="netsuite_5" width="543" height="454" loading="lazy"></p> <h3>6) Decide which data you want to import</h3> <p>Once the NetSuite integration is authorised, you can close the pop-up window and should see Step 1 of our integration settings. Please check that the name of the company listed matches your choice. </p> <p>We allow you to decide which information you wish to import into HedgeFlows. If you have outstanding invoices that were created in NetSuite several months ago, please choose the relevant historical period to load the data:</p> <h3><img src="https://help.hedgeflows.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png.png" alt="image-png" width="448" height="423" loading="lazy"></h3> <p><img src="https://help.hedgeflows.com/hs-fs/hubfs/setting_import2.png" alt="setting_import2" width="360" height="271" loading="lazy"></p> <p><img src="https://help.hedgeflows.com/hs-fs/hubfs/setting_import3.png" alt="setting_import3" width="334" height="258" loading="lazy"></p> <h3>7) Setting summary</h3> <p>Once you have confirmed your settings, you are directed to the summary screen. </p> <p><img src="https://help.hedgeflows.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Imported%20sitepage%20images/Step_5.png" alt="Step_5" width="1934" height="1140" loading="lazy"></p> <p>You can always come back to this screen and change the configuration via our Settings page.</p> <p><img src="https://help.hedgeflows.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Imported%20sitepage%20images/Settings_Config_highlighted2.png" alt="Settings_Config_highlighted2" width="1920" height="662" loading="lazy"></p> <h3>8) Finding your imported bills and invoices</h3> <p>You can locate your imported bills and invoices by navigating to the Invoices page:</p> <p><img src="https://help.hedgeflows.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Imported%20sitepage%20images/Screenshot_invoices.png" alt="Screenshot_invoices" width="3024" height="1728" loading="lazy"></p>`;
---

<PageLayout
  title="Netsuite integration - how to get started | Help Centre | HedgeFlows"
  description="Netsuite integration - how to get started - HedgeFlows Help Centre"
>
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Breadcrumb -->
      <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">
        <a href="/help" class="hover:text-brand-green transition-colors">Help Centre</a>
        <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m8.25 4.5 7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5" />
        </svg>
        <a href="/help/#integrations" class="hover:text-brand-green transition-colors">Integrations</a>
      </nav>

      <h1 class="text-[1.75rem] md:text-[2.25rem] font-bold text-text-heading leading-tight mb-8">Netsuite integration - how to get started</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-gray max-w-none
                  [&_h2]:text-2xl [&_h2]:font-bold [&_h2]:text-text-heading [&_h2]:mt-10 [&_h2]:mb-4
                  [&_h3]:text-xl [&_h3]:font-semibold [&_h3]:text-text-heading [&_h3]:mt-8 [&_h3]:mb-3
                  [&_h4]:text-lg [&_h4]:font-semibold [&_h4]:text-text-heading [&_h4]:mt-6 [&_h4]:mb-2
                  [&_p]:text-text-body [&_p]:leading-relaxed [&_p]:mb-4
                  [&_ul]:list-disc [&_ul]:pl-6 [&_ul]:mb-4 [&_ul_li]:text-text-body [&_ul_li]:mb-2
                  [&_ol]:list-decimal [&_ol]:pl-6 [&_ol]:mb-4 [&_ol_li]:text-text-body [&_ol_li]:mb-2
                  [&_a]:text-brand-green [&_a]:underline
                  [&_table]:w-full [&_table]:border-collapse [&_table]:mb-6
                  [&_th]:bg-gray-50 [&_th]:px-4 [&_th]:py-2.5 [&_th]:text-left [&_th]:text-sm [&_th]:font-semibold [&_th]:text-text-heading [&_th]:border [&_th]:border-gray-200
                  [&_td]:px-4 [&_td]:py-2.5 [&_td]:text-sm [&_td]:text-text-body [&_td]:border [&_td]:border-gray-200
                  [&_img]:rounded-xl [&_img]:shadow-sm [&_img]:my-6
                  [&_iframe]:rounded-xl [&_iframe]:my-6 [&_iframe]:w-full [&_iframe]:aspect-video">
        <Fragment set:html={articleHtml} />
      </div>

      <!-- Back link -->
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
        <a href="/help" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[0.9375rem] text-brand-green font-medium hover:underline">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 19.5 3 12m0 0 7.5-7.5M3 12h18" />
          </svg>
          Back to Help Centre
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
